<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/127215-after-being-told-this-was-an-excellent">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/127215-after-being-told-this-was-an-excellent">See all 7 answers</a>
</li>
