        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer93925269" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15388320930179094781">This is a book you should buy and not borrow from the library. Just to reward the author for such an amazing and exhilarating experience. Its as much like watching a film as it reading a book because the writing is so extraordinarily good (and clever). And this review is so dry because the author wants nothing of his book revealed. &quot;The magic is in the way the story unfolds,&quot; he&apos;s said, and yes, it is. <br/><br/>And I am <i>sooo </i>going to enjoy hand-selling people this book in my shop. I will have so many hap</span>
  <span id="freeText15388320930179094781" style="display:none">This is a book you should buy and not borrow from the library. Just to reward the author for such an amazing and exhilarating experience. Its as much like watching a film as it reading a book because the writing is so extraordinarily good (and clever). And this review is so dry because the author wants nothing of his book revealed. "The magic is in the way the story unfolds," he's said, and yes, it is. <br /><br />And I am <i>sooo </i>going to enjoy hand-selling people this book in my shop. I will have so many happy customers.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15388320930179094781" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


